## About Me
Hi there! I'm Elvinas, a third-year IT student and Software Engineer with a strong background in programming, problem-solving, and software security. I specialize in application protection, anti-tampering solutions, and anti-reverse engineering strategies.

I'm passionate about software development, game development, and tackling technical challenges. Always eager to explore new technologies and continuously apply my skills to real-world projects.

Feel free to check out my university work, personal projects, and more to see my technical expertise in action.
